		question: "Do you work with businesses in specific Carlsbad neighborhoods?",
		answer: "Yes! We optimize for specific neighborhoods like Carlsbad Village, La Costa, Bressi Ranch, Aviara, and Poinsettia. We understand each area's unique search patterns and customer demographics."
	},
	{
		question: "What industries do you specialize in for Carlsbad SEO?",
		answer: "We specialize in home service contractors (roofing, landscaping, junk removal), med spas & wellness studios, real estate agents & brokerages, cleaning companies, and local restaurants & event venues."
	},
	{
		question: "How does coastal weather and tourism affect Carlsbad SEO?",
		answer: "Carlsbad's coastal humidity, seasonal tourism, and high-income demographic make keyword seasonality crucial. We tailor campaigns to match seasonal search spikes ‚Äî like \"roof repair after winter storms\" or \"summer cleaning services Carlsbad\" ‚Äî so you always rank when customers are looking."
